           ==================================================           
=========='                                                 '===========
======           Docker & Jenkins under Supervisor               =======
==========.                                                 .===========
           ==================================================
           
           An image with Docker and Jenkins running in the
           same container.
           
           It also includes the docker plugin.




-------------------------------  Run   ---------------------------------
1. docker build --tag="docker-and-jenkins" .
2. docker run -t --privileged -p 8080:8080 docker-and-jenkins

The -t flag makes sure we can exit the container by hitting CTR+C
